an class="_ _6"></span>我都非常随喜。<span class="_ _6"></span>至于</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y186 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">其他有些行为和仪式，<span class="_ _6"></span>如果对众生有利，<span class="_ _6"></span>我们非常赞叹；<span class="_ _6"></span>若</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y17f ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">对众生没有利益，<span class="_ _8"></span>反而还会损害他们的善根，<span class="_ _8"></span>那就值得观察</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y26 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">了。 </div><div class="t m0 x67 h23 y187 ff15 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls4d ws0">（七） <span class="_ _e"> </span><span class="ff16 ls0">问<span class="ff4 fs3 ls4e">：我是哲学系的博士生。小乘佛教讲，不</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h17 y188 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">要伤害别人；<span class="_ _6"></span>大乘佛教讲，<span class="_ _6"></span>不要伤害别人的同时，<span class="_ _6"></span>还要帮助</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
